					<article class="post" id="post-77">

						<h1 class="entry-title">Service Activation Center</h1>
	
						<div class="entry-content">

							
								<p>Service Activation Center provides the tools you need to overcome typical barriers to rapid activation of new services and marketing strategies.</p>
<div class="feature-list" id="">
<div class="feature" id=""><img src="/wp-content/uploads/icon-fast-rollout.png" class="feature-icon" alt="Fast, Hassle-free Roll Out of New Services" /><div class="feature-text"><h3>Fast, Hassle-free Roll Out of New Services</h3><p>Reduce workloads of back-office system managers, customer service representatives, network operations managers, and marketing personnel.</p></div></div>
<div class="feature" id=""><img src="/wp-content/uploads/icon-streamline-operations.png" class="feature-icon" alt="Streamline Customer Service Operations" /><div class="feature-text"><h3>Streamline Customer Service Operations</h3><p>Increase efficiencies in CSR service fulfillment, from order taking, to activation, to performance verification.</p></div></div></div><div class="feature-list">
<div class="feature" id=""><img src="/wp-content/uploads/icon-capitalize.png" class="feature-icon" alt="Capitalize on New Revenue Opportunities" /><div class="feature-text"><h3>Capitalize on New Revenue Opportunities</h3><p>Supplement your post-paid billing solutions with prepaid service options.</p></div></div>
<div class="feature" id=""><img src="/wp-content/uploads/icon-increase-arpu.png" class="feature-icon" alt="Increase ARPU with Dynamic Marketing Models" /><div class="feature-text"><h3>Increase ARPU with Dynamic Marketing Models</h3><p>
Readily activate new tiers, usage-based pricing and packaging models, free trial and reduced-price incentives, and value-added applications.</p></div></div></div><div class="feature-list">
<div class="feature" id=""><img src="/wp-content/uploads/icon-self-service.png" class="feature-icon" alt="Provide Customers the Control They Want through Self-Service Options" /><div class="feature-text"><h3>Provide Customers the Control They Want through Self-Service Options</h3><p>Enable your customers to set parental controls limiting access to web sites and TV channels by category, time, or device with subscriber self-service options.</p></div></div>
<div class="feature" id=""><img src="/wp-content/uploads/icon-expansion.png" class="feature-icon" alt="Prepare for Expansion and Consolidation" /><div class="feature-text"><h3>Prepare for Expansion and Consolidation</h3><p>Support expansion and operations consolidation through multi-service activation at the regional level with full flexibility to tailor services to local requirements.</p></div></div></div><div class="feature-list">
</div>

							
						</div>

